main_body:
Decision 2005/464/EC is amended as follows:
1. in Article 1, ‘30 June 2005’ is replaced by ‘13 September 2005’;
2. in Article 3, the following point (e) is added:
‘(e) : PCR test : EUR 10 per test.’;
3. part D in the Annex is replaced by part D in the Annex to this Decision.
4. part F is added to the Annex.
